-----------------------------------------------------------------
Flyway is a database migration tool.
It helps you:
Apply changes to the database automatically
Keep track of which migrations are already applied
Maintain consistent schema across environments (dev, QA, prod)
Store all changes in version-controlled SQL files inside your project
------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Role          | Who Does What?                                           |
| ------------- | -------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Flyway**    | Handles **schema creation & versioning** using SQL files |
| **Hibernate** | Handles **data interaction** (via entities, JPA)         |
